snippet.title: The Medium - Official Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Reach beyond the limits of our reality. To a place that reflects the darkness of our world like a black mirror. Where human souls get lost and a terrifying, insidious entity lurks to prey on them. Listen to the voices, find the truth about yourself, and untangle a dark mystery that only a medium can solve.

Available now for PC and Xbox series X|S

- https://bit.ly/SteamMedium 
- https://bit.ly/MSstoreMedium
- http://bit.ly/EpicMedium

Official page: https://www.themediumgame.com 
FB: https://www.facebook.com/MediumGame/ 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TheMediumGame 
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/the_medium_... 

#TheMediumGame #BlooberTeam #LaunchTrailer
